SELECT current_year, current_month, current_day, player_id, birth_date,
  country_id, current_date, elo_rating, email, first_name, gender,
  is_email_verified, is_online, is_registered, join_date, language, last_name,
  last_played_date, mobile, p_password, password_reset_code, player_type,
  profile_pic_url, username
  FROM cs2_keyspace_5.cs2_players
  LIMIT 500;
